<m0>The poor pay<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 1.06 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>more, get less,<ql>
<m4>   LINE 2 IS .38 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>for shelter<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 3 IS 3.63 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
